'''菲蜆蝶屬'''（學名：'''''Pheles'''''）是[[蜆蝶亞科|蜆蝶亞科]][[蜆蝶族|蜆蝶族]]裡的一個[[屬|屬]]。共有8個物種，分佈於[[新熱帶界|新熱帶界]]<ref>Tree of Life Web Project. 2008. Pheles Herrich-Schaeffer 1853. Lepricornis C. Felder & R. Felder 1865 currently viewed as a subjective junior synonym, Otacustesis Dyar 1914 currently viewed as a subjective junior synonym. Version 05 June 2008 (under construction). http://tolweb.org/Pheles/104662/2008.06.05 in The Tree of Life Web Project, http://tolweb.org/ {{Wayback|url=http://tolweb.org/ |date=20110515100516 }} {{en}}</ref>。外型[[擬態|擬態]]模仿各種[[綃蝶族|綃蝶]]。

